{"tid":1571260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日因為資訊唔流通，魔法爭啲扔到消防員","createTime":"2019-09-15T11:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T11:49:26.000Z","uid":90486,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c104f48099f3220b0b22acdb67d1bf71cda7bd7","tid":1571260,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"隔住水馬，手足睇唔到入面咩情況，上面手足見到正前方係消防，左前方先係差佬，但前線照扔魔法去前方。<br />\n<br />\n戴住豬咀講野好細聲，現場又好多煙除唔到，前線唔會睇到電話，可以點拆？<br />\n<br />\n我建議哨可以用laser燈做指示（藍色攻擊點、紅色係危險地方etc)，前線可以睇住嚟換位<br />\n<br />\n開放討論"},{"pid":"39701226c442a04f2ff0a5bd97d6dde6cd912945","tid":1571260,"uid":15971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:25:42.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"94eb44cd8ba556e3dc0822169d4b21cd51943ef9","tid":1571260,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70dde95a85e2dbe8af428e3597760b1be358e8eb","tid":1571260,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:28:43.000Z","msg":"集火"},{"pid":"27aaf1984c146ea9875b4f49ddf1068b779bc234","tid":1571260,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"戰術討論，比啲意見"},{"pid":"4562be3525818d515bea06cd542cf2198179671a","tid":1571260,"uid":31022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea08ede4db34a167b46c0c687b832550b7cf49a1","tid":1571260,"uid":90486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"有無其他野可以代替laser, 或者將指示整成旗，組前線旗隊"}]}